dct_description_sm: "Turkey in Europe" territory predates Russo-Turkish War (1877-1878), and Sakhalin Island is shown on map under the same color as Russian mainland (Treaty of St. Petersburg 1875)--dating this map between 1875 and 1878.
Shows territories (distinguished by coloring, dotted lines), waterways, cities and regions.
